### Debug RxDB Replication Infinite Loops with error$

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/replication.html

This code snippet demonstrates how to subscribe to the `error$` observable of an RxReplicationState to debug infinite replication loops or unexpected HTTP request re-runs. This is useful when the pull-handler might be crashing.

```typescript
myRxReplicationState.error$.subscribe(err => console.log('error$', err))
```

