### RxDB Bulk Insert vs. Single Inserts

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/nosql-performance-tips.html

Demonstrates the correct and incorrect ways to insert multiple documents into an RxDB collection. Using `bulkInsert` is significantly more performant than individual `insert` calls within a loop.

```javascript
// wrong ❌
for(const docData of dataAr){
    await myCollection.insert(docData);
}
// right ✔️
await myCollection.bulkInsert(dataAr);
```

