### Explicitly Commit IndexedDB Transaction

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/slow-indexeddb.html

This JavaScript code demonstrates how to explicitly commit an IndexedDB transaction. It includes a check to ensure the `commit()` method is available on the transaction object before calling it, providing a slight performance improvement by avoiding implicit commits.

```javascript
// .commit() is not available on all browsers, so first check if it exists.
if (transaction.commit) {
    transaction.commit()
}
```

