### RxDB: Query Undone Todos Locally

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs-src/docs/articles/local-first-future.md

Queries the 'todos' collection in RxDB to find all documents where the 'done' field is false. This demonstrates how to perform local queries on the database without network latency.

```typescript
const remaining = await db.todos.find({
  selector: { done: { $eq: false } }
}).exec();
console.log(`Remaining todos: ${remaining.length}`);
```
